{"tid":1270940,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"警犬：示威者向警務人員投擲懷疑含有不知名液體物件","createTime":"2019-07-01T03:59:05.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-01T04:43:03.000Z","uid":216992,"like":1,"dislike":16,"uniUserReply":21,"replies":[{"pid":"a9ee2923337ef28dba55a2c51b4afa346b741ab3","tid":1270940,"uid":216992,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-01T03:59:05.000Z","msg":"　　今日（七月一日）在示威者堵塞龍和道、添美道及夏愨道一帶並衝擊警方防線期間，於上午約九時三十分，有示威者向在場警務人員投擲懷疑含有不知名液體的物件，令現場警務人員受傷。當中有人員呼吸困難及皮膚紅腫，共十三名警務人員已送院接受治療。案件交由有組織罪案及三合會調查科跟進。警方強烈譴責示威者有關行為，必定會嚴肅跟進。<br />\n<br />\n　　警方警告示威者立刻停止使用暴力並盡快離開。由於灣仔金鐘一帶情況混亂，警方呼籲市民暫時不要前往該區。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/(null\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2F%28null&d=YBElpbzmALMQinc%2Bu7edPwxAEvDk8dns9g3QPAGj3dU%3D&h=6e582acb\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/(null</a>)?metadata=HrTP3NwV2NR7C58SIn4dxWXqcXtWqmSyrN69GFIrQqVcleYfxv6rv53uUZVXYjNiEWTy+H10Lt3n7z3Vrb4C6ZZiG96QsL09&amp;sfns=mo"},{"pid":"80a363eda875827386899b1613c0b41c934fc914","tid":1270940,"uid":216992,"like":1,"dislike":10,"score":-9,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-01T04:00:08.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.info.gov.hk/gia/general/201907/01/P2019070100365.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.info.gov.hk%2Fgia%2Fgeneral%2F201907%2F01%2FP2019070100365.htm&d=YBElpbzmALMQinc%2Bu7edPwxAEvDk8dns9g3QPAGj3dU%3D&h=f007891b\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.info.gov.hk/gia/general/201907/01/P2019070100365.htm</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/PNPopWm.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FPNPopWm.png&h=1c80ceff&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"eeb41c933c5a2b9cd28b0c867ad379960160b5d2","tid":1270940,"uid":62837,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-01T04:01:27.000Z","msg":"太暴力了<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4096e7d9ee20774eda7875e